How to play the game:


Rule:
Winner is the first player to get an unbroken row of four leds horizontally,vertically,or diagonally.

Tie could be make when all the matrix is fulled with out any player connected to 4.



Choose led:
Press the navigational switch up(North): row ++.
press the navigational switch down(South) : row--;
Press the navigational switch right(East): column ++.
press the navigational switch left(West) : column--;
press the navigational switch push: flash the corresponding on another player's board.

Display led matrix:
Setted led will not flash.
Received led will flash.

Others:
If player want to set unavailable led(The led is setted or received),when press the navigational switch push, the led will not flash on another player's board.




